                  <lb/>
The manner of his resurrection<lb/>
so miraculous and ineffable,<lb/>
that <normalised orig="bad" auto="true">bade</normalised> words express<lb/>
it best. In a moral relation<lb/>
to the <normalised orig="Jewes" auto="true">Jews</normalised>, it is here<lb/>
                  <pb n="59"/>
                  <lb/>
