but the moral evil of<lb/>
it reflected upon others.<lb/>
                  <pb n="60"/>
                  <lb/>
The Law saith, he steals<lb/>
who fraudulently takes away<lb/>
something of <normalised orig="anothers" auto="true">another</normalised>,<lb/>
with intent to get the thing<lb/>
it self, its use or possession; <lb/>
if this definition be true, his<lb/>
